#: src/Dialogs/dlgGestureHelp.cpp:16
msgid ""
"# Gesture Navigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen "
"mode\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan "
"mode\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby "
"waypoints."
msgstr ""
"# Gestensteuerung\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar unterstützt Touch-Gesten auf der Karte:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Nach oben wischen** (U): Hineinzoomen\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Nach unten wischen** (D): Herauszoomen\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Nach rechts wischen** (R): Vorheriger "
"Bildschirmmodus\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Nach links wischen** (L): Nächster "
"Bildschirmmodus\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Oben-Unten** (UD): Autozoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Unten-Oben** (DU): Menü\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Unten-Rechts** (DR): Wegpunktdetails\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Unten-Links** (DL): Alternativen\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Rechts-Unten** (RD): Aufgabenmanager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Oben-Rechts-Unten** (URD): Analyse\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Links-Unten-Rechts** (LDR): Checkliste\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Oben-Rechts-Unten-Links** (URDL): Pan-"
"Modus\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Links-Unten-Rechts-Unten-Links** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Oben-Links-Unten-Rechts** (ULDR): "
"Schnellmenü\n"
"\n"
"Durch langes Tippen auf die Karte aktivierst du den Pan-Modus. Tippe im Pan-"
"Modus, um nahegelegene Wegpunkte zu sehen."

